---
description: Constraints for Supabase SQL migrations — append-only, RLS + grants required.
globs: supabase/migrations/**,supabase/**/*.sql
alwaysApply: false
---

# Supabase migrations

- Migrations are append-only. Do not rewrite already-applied migration files; add a new file instead.
- Every new table: enable RLS, add policies, and `grant` to `anon`/`authenticated` as needed.
- Dashboard-only schema edits are not source of truth — encode changes in `supabase/migrations/`.
- Prefer the `supabase-migration` skill for the full checklist.
